metadata.name: immortal
metadata.description:
every story has a beginning and an end, 
that's just human nature.

their story has a beginning indeed but only they know there's no end, endless stories one after another. 
thousand lives, millions maybe.  
at the very beginning they were born as royalty, 
they had no idea about other lives then. 
they died and came back as a homeless. 
first they had a family, after they don't. 
they were "he" once, right before being "they".

they know how deeply other people want to live forever,  
they also know how it feels to live forever.  
when it ends once, 
they came with memories but nothing else.  
with different languages in different countries, 
with different opportunities in different environments.  
but still,  
there's no endless wealth, 
no endless love, 
no endless stories. 
but there's an endless pain cause of all memories.
